cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the design of a security architecture for the Internet of Things (IoT), which involves wireless communication and network design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
